The national team caused the biggest upset in the Africa Cup of Nations (Afcon) when they beat Egypt 1-0 in front of a capacity crowd last Saturday. Lorch scored the only goal that took Bafana Bafana to the quarterfinals. Bafana will play against their biggest nemesis Nigeria in a crucial quarter-final match on Wednesday night. Kick-off at 21:00 live on SABC 3. The two nations have played against each other 13 times since SA was re-admitted into international football.
--SABC--